CBRE is delighted to offer 19 Jordan Close, Altona, for lease.

19 Jordan Close, Altona is situated in Altona’s industrial precinct just off Kororoit Creek Road. In the industrial market, Altona’s postcode is looked on favourably amongst occupiers due to its proximity to Melbourne’s key infrastructure nodes.  

Jordan Close offers ease of access to the wider western freeway network via Kororoit Creek Road, Grieve Parade or Millers Road. The neighbouring residential population – less than 300m - provides a local workforce and associated shops/amenity for your staff. 

2.2km to Princes Freeway on/off ramp
10km to the Port of Melbourne
13km to Melbourne CBD

+ Total building area of 1,135sqm*

+ Overhead crane spanning full length and width of warehouse
